{"id":"fb7e2f90-8fd5-4022-9c0d-64032f53c58c","name":"Dragon Ball S.H. Figuarts Bulma's Motorcycle with Goku 17cm (New)","slug":"dragon-ball-s.h.-figuarts-bulma's-motorc","description":"<p><strong>Dragon Ball</strong> Figure of <strong>Bulma's Motorcycle with Goku</strong>, size approx.17cm. <strong>Official product</strong> by <strong>Tamashii Nations.</strong></p>\n<p>From the first episode of \"Dragon Ball\", the <b>bike</b> on <b>Bulma</b> was riding appeared on <b>S.H.Figuarts</b>!<br /><br />The roof panel and turn signal, head tale lamp are molded in translucent plastic. The frame, front fork, muffler, and footrests are all made of diecast metal, giving the bike a satisfying sense of weight. It even comes with a display stand featuring the <b>Capsule Corp</b>. logo. It also includes an in-scale Goku. Plus, the stand lets you pose the bike statically, as if riding, or popping a wheelie! The set includes the motorcycle, a stand set, optional skirt and  pair of optional hands(L/R) for <b>S.H.Figuarts Bulma</b>, and Non-movable <b>Son Goku</b> figure.<br /><br />Products other than S.H.Figuarts BULMAS MOTORCYCLE-HOIPOI CAPSULE No.9- is sold separately.<br /><br /></p>","metaTitle":null,"metaDescription":null,"model":null,"releaseDate":null,"image":null,"condition":null,"edition":null,"rarity":null,"features":null,"specifications":null,"createdAt":"2025-03-25T23:58:06.361Z","updatedAt":"2025-03-25T23:58:06.361Z","barcode":"4573102587398","deletedAt":null,"brandId":"3973100e-a304-42f2-b48a-5e810adf1082","franchiseId":null,"seriesId":null,"lineId":null,"categories":[{"productId":"fb7e2f90-8fd5-4022-9c0d-64032f53c58c","categoryId":"bc7dcae3-c133-443f-85e0-737ca2ab3570","category":{"id":"bc7dcae3-c133-443f-85e0-737ca2ab3570","name":"Collectibles","slug":"collectibles","description":"Auto-imported category: Collectibles","image":null,"parentId":null,"createdAt":"2025-03-25T22:47:04.384Z","updatedAt":"2025-03-25T22:47:04.384Z","deletedAt":null}}],"retailerPrices":[{"id":